dataSource.select: SELECT type , libbr, libdir, libpole, codsg, socfact, rnom, ident, lmoisprest, factcodsg, numfact, codcompta, fact_total, conso_tot, numcont, conso, conso_expense, cout, montant_mens, rtype, numexpense FROM (select '1' type, br.codbr codbr, dir.coddir coddir, br.libbr libbr, dir.libdir libdir, s.sigdep||'/'||s.sigpole libpole, r.codsg codsg, r.soccode socfact, r.rnom rnom, r.ident ident, r.lmoisprest lmoisprest, NULL factcodsg, 'TOTAL' as numfact, NULL codcompta, r.fact_total fact_total, DECODE(r.montant_mensuel,NULL,r.conso_total*r.cout,r.montant_mensuel) conso_tot, NULL numcont, r.conso_total conso, TO_NUMBER(NULL) conso_expense, r.cout cout, r.montant_mensuel montant_mens, res.rtype rtype, NULL numexpense from faccons_ressource r, struct_info s, directions dir, branches br, datdebex,vue_dpg_perime VDP, ressource res where r.codsg = s.codsg AND r.ident = res.ident(+) and s.coddir = dir.coddir and dir.codbr = br.codbr AND s.codsg =VDP.codsg AND INSTR(:P_PERIME, VDP.codbddpg) > 0 AND to_char(r.lmoisprest,'YYYY')=decode(:p_param7,'N',to_char(datdebex,'YYYY'),to_char(to_number(to_char(datdebex,'YYYY'))-1)) AND 1<(SELECT count(*) from faccons_facture f2 WHERE f2.lmoisprest=r.lmoisprest AND f2.ident=r.ident) UNION select '2' type, br.codbr codbr, dir.coddir coddir, br.libbr libbr, dir.libdir libdir, s.sigdep||'/'||s.sigpole libpole, r.codsg codsg, f.socfact socfact, r.rnom rnom, r.ident ident, r.lmoisprest lmoisprest, to_char(f.codsg) factcodsg, f.numfact numfact, f.codcompta codcompta, decode(f.typfact,'A',-1,1)*f.montht fact_total, TO_NUMBER(NULL) conso_tot, rpad(f.numcont,27,' ')||f.cav numcont, TO_NUMBER(NULL) conso, f.cusag_expense conso_exepense, TO_NUMBER(NULL) cout, TO_NUMBER(NULL) montant_mens, res.rtype rtype, fact.num_expense numexpense from faccons_ressource r, struct_info s,vue_dpg_perime VDP, datdebex,directions dir, branches br, faccons_facture f, ressource res, facture fact where r.ident=f.ident(+) and r.lmoisprest=f.lmoisprest(+) and r.ident=res.ident(+) and r.codsg=s.codsg and s.coddir=dir.coddir and dir.codbr=br.codbr and f.numfact=fact.numfact(+) and f.typfact=fact.typfact(+) and f.socfact=fact.socfact(+) and f.datfact=fact.datfact(+) --AND (f.codcompta IN ('6391504','6391506','6396206','6391503') or f.codcompta is null) AND s.codsg =VDP.codsg AND INSTR(:P_PERIME, VDP.codbddpg) > 0 AND to_char(r.lmoisprest,'YYYY')=decode(:p_param7,'N',to_char(datdebex,'YYYY'),to_char(to_number(to_char(datdebex,'YYYY'))-1)) AND 1<(SELECT count(*) from faccons_facture f2 WHERE f2.lmoisprest=f.lmoisprest AND f2.ident=f.ident) UNION select '1' type, br.codbr codbr, dir.coddir coddir, br.libbr libbr, dir.libdir libdir, s.sigdep||'/'||s.sigpole libpole, r.codsg codsg, r.soccode socfact, r.rnom rnom, r.ident ident, r.lmoisprest lmoisprest, to_char(f.codsg) factcodsg, f.numfact numfact, f.codcompta codcompta, decode(f.typfact,'A',-1,1)*f.montht fact_total, DECODE(r.montant_mensuel,NULL,r.conso_total*r.cout,r.montant_mensuel) conso_tot, f.numcont || f.cav numcont, r.conso_total conso, f.cusag_expense conso_expense, r.cout cout, r.montant_mensuel montant_mens, res.rtype rtype, fact.num_expense numexpense from faccons_ressource r, struct_info s,vue_dpg_perime VDP, datdebex, directions dir, branches br, faccons_facture f, ressource res, facture fact where r.ident=f.ident(+) and r.lmoisprest=f.lmoisprest(+) and r.ident=res.ident(+) and r.codsg=s.codsg and f.numfact=fact.numfact(+) and f.typfact=fact.typfact(+) and f.socfact=fact.socfact(+) and f.datfact=fact.datfact(+) and s.coddir=dir.coddir and dir.codbr=br.codbr -- AND (f.codcompta IN ('6391504','6391506','6396206','6391503') or f.codcompta is null) AND s.codsg =VDP.codsg AND INSTR(:P_PERIME, VDP.codbddpg) > 0 AND to_char(r.lmoisprest,'YYYY')=decode(:p_param7,'N',to_char(datdebex,'YYYY'),to_char(to_number(to_char(datdebex,'YYYY'))-1)) AND 1>=(SELECT count(*) from faccons_facture f2 WHERE f2.lmoisprest=f.lmoisprest AND f2.ident=f.ident) ) order by codbr ASC, coddir ASC, codsg ASC, socfact ASC, rnom ASC, ident ASC, lmoisprest ASC, type ASC, fact_total DESC, numfact ASC ;
